b'Nemurenu Yoru no Chiisana Ohanashi': b"Three videos about cats--Cat's Best Friend, Cat's Adventure, and Cat's Christmas-each containing three smaller stories of feline fun. Based on a 1989 column in Monthly Kadokawa magazine by Yuko Hara, better known as the keyboard player/vocalist with the Southern All-Stars.\n\n(Source: The Anime Encyclopedia)"
